data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This property meets $0 down requirements, USDA loan requirements for those qualified. Save on property taxes, located in Medina County! This stunning move-in ready home is a perfect blend of modern convenience & timeless elegance. Home features the Master on main floor, granite countertops, ceramic tile & carpet, includes water softener & reverse osmosis system, stainless steel refrigerator, and washer & dryer. Enjoy the luxury of space with generously sized rooms with walk-in closets that cater to your family's every need. A two-car garage with extra storage space ensures that your vehicles and belongings are comfortably accommodated. Embrace sustainable living with solar panels that not only reduce your carbon footprint but also contribute to significant savings on energy bill. Walking distance to elementary and middle schools, minutes to H-E-B Plus, community pool, playground, sports court, and a dog park. Schedule a viewing today!
